Trent Alexander-Arnold scored with a great free kick
Declan Rice chipped in with a goal to make sure of the win
Arttu Hoskonen got a late consolation for the hosts
Pre-Game Insights: Manager Lee Carsley opted for a more coherent formation, helped in part by the return of striker Harry Kane
Noni Madueke came on for Palmer midway through the second half; Levi Colwill was an unused substitute
Post-Match Reflections: Lee Carsley has now got three wins from his four games in charge and has at least shown a willingness to try some new things
